#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Referencing the default truststore of SunJSSE"
msgstr "引用 SunJSSE 的默认信任存储"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"JDK distributions typically contain a truststore in the `$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts` file.\n"
"SunJSSE uses this truststore as the default truststore.\n"
"SunJSSE is the default implementation of the Java Secure Socket Extension (JSSE)."
msgstr "JDK 发行版通常在 `$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts` 文件中包含一个信任库。SunJSSE 将该信任库用作默认信任库。SunJSSE 是 Java 安全套接字扩展 (JSSE) 的默认实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Java runtime components, such as `javax.net.ssl.HttpsURLConnection`, rely on JSSE for SSL and TLS."
msgstr "Java 运行时组件（如 `javax.net.ssl.HttpsURLConnection` ）依靠 JSSE 实现 SSL 和 TLS。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Although Quarkus extensions typically do not honor the default truststore of SunJSSE, it is still practical to use it in some situations.\n"
"This applies when migrating from legacy technologies or running on a Linux distribution where the SunJSSE truststore is synchronized with the operating system (OS)."
msgstr "尽管 Quarkus 扩展通常不采用 SunJSSE 的默认信任库，但在某些情况下使用它仍然是实用的。这适用于从传统技术迁移或在 Linux 发行版上运行时，SunJSSE 信任库与操作系统（OS）同步。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To simplify the use of the SunJSSE truststore, Quarkus TLS Registry provides a TLS configuration under the name `javax.net.ssl` that mimics the default behavior of SunJSSE:"
msgstr "为了简化 SunJSSE 信任存储的使用，Quarkus TLS 注册表提供了一个 TLS 配置，名称为 `javax.net.ssl` ，它模仿了 SunJSSE 的默认行为："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the `javax.net.ssl.trustStore` system property is defined, its value is honored as a truststore."
msgstr "如果定义了 `javax.net.ssl.trustStore` 系统属性，则其值将作为信任存储被使用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Otherwise, the paths `$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/jssecacerts` and `$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts` are checked, and the first existing file is used as a truststore."
msgstr "否则，将检查路径 `$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/jssecacerts` 和 `$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts` ，并将第一个现有文件用作信任存储。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If neither condition is met, an `IllegalStateException` is thrown."
msgstr "如果两个条件都不满足，则会抛出 `IllegalStateException` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The password to open the truststore is obtained from the `javax.net.ssl.trustStorePassword` system property.\n"
"If this property is not set, the default password `changeit` is used."
msgstr "打开信任存储的密码来自 `javax.net.ssl.trustStorePassword` 系统属性。如果未设置该属性，则使用默认密码 `changeit` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `javax.net.ssl` configuration can be used as a value for various `*.tls-configuration-name` properties, as shown below:"
msgstr "`javax.net.ssl` 配置可用作各种 `*.tls-configuration-name` 属性的值，如下所示："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `javax.net.ssl` TLS configuration can not be customized or overridden."
msgstr "`javax.net.ssl` TLS 配置不可定制或重写。"

#. type: Title =
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuring TLS"
msgstr "配置 TLS"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"TLS configuration primarily involves managing keystores and truststores.\n"
"The specific setup depends on the format used, such as PEM, P12, or JKS."
msgstr "TLS 配置主要涉及管理密钥库和信任库。具体设置取决于所使用的格式，如 PEM、P12 或 JKS。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The following sections outline the available TLS configuration properties."
msgstr "以下各节概述了可用的 TLS 配置属性。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Key stores"
msgstr "主要商店"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Key stores store private keys and certificates.\n"
"They are mainly used on the server side, but can also be used on the client side when mTLS is used."
msgstr "密钥库存储私钥和证书。它们主要用于服务器端，但在使用 mTLS 时也可用于客户端。"

#. type: Title ===
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "PEM keystores"
msgstr "PEM 密钥存储"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Privacy Enhanced Mail (PEM) keystores are composed of a list of file pairs:"
msgstr "隐私增强邮件 (PEM) 密钥存储由一系列文件对组成："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*The certificate file* - a `.crt` or `.pem` file."
msgstr "*证书文件* - `.crt` 或 `.pem` 文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*The private key file* - often a `.key` file."
msgstr "*私钥文件* --通常是 `.key` 文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To configure a PEM keystore:"
msgstr "配置 PEM 密钥存储："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In most cases, you only need a single pair consisting of a certificate and a private key.\n"
"Even if the certificate is part of a certificate chain, it includes only one private key that corresponds to the end-entity certificate."
msgstr "在大多数情况下，你只需要由证书和私钥组成的单一配对。即使证书是证书链的一部分，它也只包括一个与终端实体证书相对应的私钥。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When multiple pairs are configured, the selection of one of the configured pairs of certificates and private keys is based on Server Name Indication (SNI).\n"
"The client sends the name of the server to which the client is attempting to connect, and the server selects the appropriate pair of certificates and private keys.\n"
"To use this feature, ensure that xref:./tls-registry-reference.adoc#sni[SNI] is enabled on both the client and server."
msgstr "如果配置了多对证书和私钥，则根据服务器名称指示（SNI）选择其中一对证书和私钥。客户端发送试图连接的服务器名称，服务器就会选择相应的证书和私钥对。要使用此功能，请确保客户端和服务器都启用了 xref:./tls-registry-reference.adoc#sni[SNI] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When configuring multiple key pairs or certificate pairs, the server executes the configured pairs in a lexicographical order of their names by default, as demonstrated with `store.pem.a` and `store.pem.b` in the previous example.\n"
"The pair with the lowest lexicographical order is executed first.\n"
"To change this, you can define the order by using the `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.order` property.\n"
"For example, `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.order=b,c,a`."
msgstr "配置多个密钥对或证书对时，服务器默认按名称的词序执行配置的密钥对，如上例 `store.pem.a` 和 `store.pem.b` 所示。具有最低词典顺序的配对将首先执行。要更改顺序，可以使用 `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.order` 属性定义顺序。例如， `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.order=b,c,a` ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This setting is important when using SNI, because it uses the first specified pair as the default."
msgstr "该设置在使用 SNI 时非常重要，因为它会使用第一个指定的配对作为默认值。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When using a PEM keystore, the following formats are supported:"
msgstr "使用 PEM 密钥存储时，支持以下格式："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "PKCS#8 private key (unencrypted)"
msgstr "PKCS#8 私钥（未加密）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "PKCS#1 RSA private key (unencrypted)"
msgstr "PKCS#1 RSA 私钥（未加密）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Encrypted PKCS#8 private key (encrypted with AES-128-CBC)"
msgstr "加密的 PKCS#8 私钥（使用 AES-128-CBC 加密）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For an encrypted PKCS#8 private key, set the `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.password` or `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.<name>.password` property to the password that decrypts the private key."
msgstr "对于加密的 PKCS#8 私钥，将 `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.password` 或 `quarkus.tls.key-store.pem.<name>.password` 属性设置为解密私钥的密码。"

#. type: Block title
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An encrypted PEM keystore configuration example:"
msgstr "加密 PEM 密钥存储配置示例："

#. type: Title ===
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "PKCS12 keystores"
msgstr "PKCS12 密钥存储"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "PKCS12 keystores are single files that contain the certificate and the private key."
msgstr "PKCS12 密钥存储是包含证书和私钥的单一文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To configure a PKCS12 keystore:"
msgstr "配置 PKCS12 密钥存储："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`.p12` files are password-protected, so you need to provide the password to open the keystore."
msgstr "`.p12` 文件受密码保护，因此需要提供密码才能打开密钥存储。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These files can contain multiple certificates and private keys.\n"
"If this is the case, take either of the following actions:"
msgstr "这些文件可能包含多个证书和私钥。如果是这种情况，请执行以下任一操作："

#. type: Plain text
