msgstr "PKCS12 信托库"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"PKCS12 truststores are single-file containers for certificates.\n"
"You can use the alias to select the appropriate certificate when multiple certificates are included."
msgstr "PKCS12 信任库是证书的单一文件容器。当包含多个证书时，可以使用别名来选择相应的证书。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
